/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock
# EXCEPT the firmware binary's lockfile: the flashed image must be reproducible
# from the repo (it carries a vendored, patched cyw43 — see kiln-firmware/vendor).
!kiln-firmware/Cargo.lock

# Device runtime config — holds WiFi credentials (like config.py). Keep
# config.example.json in the repo; generate config.json locally for deploy.
config.json
